data.title: Gaerne MTB Trophy 2022 - Master
data.meta_description: Gaerne MTB Trophy 2022 - Master - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides results from the X Gaerne Mountain Bike Trophy Grand Prix D'Inverno race. Mattia Finazzi of Italy finished first in the M1 category with a time of 1 hour, 26 minutes and 10.4 seconds. Andrea Bravin of Italy finished second, 1 minute and 57.8 seconds behind Finazzi. The fastest lap was ridden by Mattia Finazzi in 16 minutes and 34.5 seconds.
